"Spell of Duplication

Place the archetype on the altar and perform incantations VI and VII as described in section c) of the appendix. The spell will build up as long as the archetype stays on the altar. Remove the archetype after the appropriate time and stand aside to let the duplicates take shape.

Before invoking this spell, ensure that the surroundings are cleared and allow enough space for the duplicates to appear.
Do not allow the archetype to rest on the altar for too long.

To reverse the spell, place the first created duplicate on the altar. Only the archetype will remain."